"title": "5864: futility",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5864: futility",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>All human life and human systems are ultimately useless without God, because death comes to all. God wants to deliver people from their futile ways.</p>\n<h2>Human life is futile</h2>\n<h3>The brevity of life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:47\">PSA 89:47</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job7:6-Job7:7\">JOB 7:6–7:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job14:1-Job14:2\">JOB 14:1–14:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:4-Ps39:5\">PSA 39:4–39:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl6:12\">ECC 6:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:6-Isa40:7\">ISA 40:6–40:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:14\">JAS 4:14</a></p>\n<h3>Death is the destiny of all</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job9:22\">JOB 9:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl3:19-Eccl3:20\">ECC 3:19–3:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:2\">ECC 9:2</a></p>\n<h3>The dead are forgotten</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:15-Ps103:16\">PSA 103:15–103:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl1:11\">ECC 1:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:16\">ECC 2:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl9:5\">ECC 9:5</a></p>\n<h2>Human endeavour is futile</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl1:14\">ECC 1:14</a></strong> <em>The writer speaks of human life without reference to God.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps39:6\">PSA 39:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps127:2\">PSA 127:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl2:10-Eccl2:23\">ECC 2:10–2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hab2:13\">HAB 2:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:11\">JAS 1:11</a></p>\n<h2>Human thoughts are futile</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:11\">PSA 94:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:19-1Cor3:20\">1CO 3:19–3:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:21\">ROM 1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:17-Eph4:18\">EPH 4:17–4:18</a></p>\n<h2>Human attitudes are futile</h2>\n<h3>Self-confidence is futile</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa16:6\">ISA 16:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer48:29-Jer48:30\">JER 48:29–48:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:51-Luke1:52\">LUK 1:51–1:52</a></p>\n<h3>Relying solely on human help is futile</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer17:5\">JER 17:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps60:11\">PSA 60:11</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps108:12\">PSA 108:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:3-Ps146:4\">PSA 146:3–146:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa2:22\">ISA 2:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:1-Isa30:5\">ISA 30:1–30:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa31:1-Isa31:3\">ISA 31:1–31:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam4:17\">LAM 4:17</a></p>\n<h2>False religion is futile</h2>\n<h3>Idolatry is futile</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:15\">2KI 17:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:21\">1SA 12:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps31:6\">PSA 31:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:5\">JER 2:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:8\">JER 10:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:14-Jer10:15\">JER 10:14–10:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer16:19\">JER 16:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jonah2:8\">JON 2:8</a></p>\n<h3>Divination is futile</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa8:19-Isa8:22\">ISA 8:19–8:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek13:6-Ezek13:9\">EZK 13:6–13:9</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech10:2\">ZEC 10:2</a></p>\n<h3>Human religious systems are futile</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:29\">1KI 18:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa16:12\">ISA 16:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:5\">JER 10:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:36-Acts5:38\">ACT 5:36–5:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:20-Col2:23\">COL 2:20–2:23</a></p>\n<h2>Nominal religion is futile</h2>\n<h3>Religious observance without true faith is futile</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:13\">ISA 1:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:14\">MAL 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:8-Matt15:9\">MAT 15:8–15:9</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:6-Mark7:7\">MRK 7:6–7:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:1-1Cor3:3\">1CO 3:1–3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:26\">JAS 1:26</a></p>\n<h3>Mere religious language is futile</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:9\">TIT 3:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:8\">JER 7:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam2:14\">LAM 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:6\">EPH 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:18\">COL 2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:6\">1TI 1:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:14\">2TI 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:18\">2PE 2:18</a></p>\n<h3>Christian endeavour using only human strength is futile</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:5\">JHN 15:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor3:12-1Cor3:15\">1CO 3:12–3:15</a></p>\n<h3>Hearing God's word without responding to it is futile</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:2\">HEB 4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:26-Matt7:27\">MAT 7:26–7:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:19-Matt13:22\">MAT 13:19–13:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:22-Jas1:24\">JAS 1:22–1:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:20\">JAS 2:20</a></p>\n<h2>Sin is futile because it achieves nothing</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer13:10\">JER 13:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps2:1\">PSA 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps112:10\">PSA 112:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:118\">PSA 119:118</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:28\">PRO 10:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov11:7\">PRO 11:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:58\">JER 51:58</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:11\">EPH 5:11</a></p>\n<h2>Faithfulness to God may seem to be futile</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps73:13\">PSA 73:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job34:9\">JOB 34:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl7:15\">ECC 7:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl8:14\">ECC 8:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa49:4\">ISA 49:4</a></p>\n<h2>God wants to deliver people from futile ways</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:18\">1PE 1:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:21\">2TI 2:21</a></p>",
